		<title lang="en"><![CDATA[Topic Preview - jQuery (mb)Tooltip Style Add-On for Board3 Portal]]></title>
		<description lang="en"><![CDATA[Uses jQuery and the (mb)Tooltip plug-in to create a nicer looking Topic Preview. These instructions add this feature to Board3 Portal installations.]]></description>
		<author-notes lang="en"><![CDATA[Use of these instructions requires that you have already installed:
-Board3 Portal (v2.0.X)
-Topic Preview
-Topic Preview for Board3 Portal add-on
-jQuery (mb)Tooltip style for Topic Preview add-on]]></author-notes>
